{
  "stem": "4764.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, they gave us things, and-- and all of a sudden it was-- it was just-- just so different.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- And my father said that he was-- he was very happy now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't understand why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, I couldn't see anything different apart from different looking people running around carrying on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he seemed to think that they were-- they were the ant's pants.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, he-- he got along with this captain very well because they were both army men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he seemed to get along with him like-- like he was some long lost brother, or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I couldn't quite figure out what the hell was going on because they were so chummy all of a sudden.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the people seemed to be-- you know, my mother seemed to be happier than she'd ever been, and it just seemed completely different.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I couldn't quite figure out what the hell was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I didn't understand what it meant, that they said, well, as far as they were concerned, the war was finished.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I didn't know what that meant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because I'd never experienced anything else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The war was war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was there forever, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I couldn't quite understand what that actually meant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But then they were very-- then they seemed to be very upset again because they hadn't heard about any of their relatives.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I think they tried to get-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'm not sure whether they tried to get some sort of information out of-- but anyway, the news was bad, that there was no one left.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then we left Hungary, for some reason or other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a very nice guy.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
